snippet.title: Valkyria Chronicles 4 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Take command of Squad E and lead them to victory in their fight against the Imperial Army. 

Valkyria Chronicles 4 now on PS4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, and PC. Order your copy today at http://valkyria.sega.com/
